<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.1">
<l>kiṭanta nampi kuṭantai mēvik kēḻa lāyulakai</l>
<l>yiṭanta nampi yeṅkaḷ nampi yeṟiña raraṇaḻiya</l>
<l>kaṭanta nampi kaṭiyā rilaṅkai yulakai yīraṭiyāl</l>
<l>naṭanta nampi nāmañ collil namōnā rāyaṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you say a name of the noble who reclines dwelling in Kuṭantai,</l>
<l>The noble who dug up the earth as a boar, our noble,</l>
<l>The noble who overcame well-protected Laṅkā</l>
<l rend="indent">to destroy the enemy defenses,</l>
<l>The noble who walked the world with two steps,</l>
<l rend="indent">[that itself is] the Namō Nārāyaṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
